name: OSXCollector
description: Runs OSXCollector on an endpoint running OS X

actions.description: Get information about a system using OSXCollector
actions.verbose:
This action will only work on an endpoint running OS X.
This action will create a copy of the osxcollector.py file in the endpoint's /tmp/phantom directory.
Sections are a way to filter out the data. For a list of sections, refer to this link: https://github.com/Yelp/osxcollector.
Due to the large amount of data and time involved, this app does not support running with the 'full_hash' section.

sections.description: A comma seperated list of sections
